et\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Benjamin Becker]]\n|1\u20136, 4\u20136\n|-\n|bgcolor=#98fb98|Win\n|<small>7\u20133</small>\n|[[2013 Sparkasse ATP Challenger \u2013 Singles|{{dts|Nov 2013}}]]\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|[[Internazionali Tennis Val Gardena S\u00fcdtirol|Ortisei]], Italy\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|Challenger\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Simon Greul]]\n|7\u20136<sup>(7\u20134)</sup>, 6\u20132\n|-\n|bgcolor=#98fb98|Win\n|<small>8\u20133</small>\n|[[2014 Sparkassen ATP Challenger \u2013 Singles|{{dts|Nov 2014}}]]\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|[[Internazionali Tennis Val Gardena S\u00fcdtirol|Ortisei]], Italy\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|Challenger\n|Hard (i)\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Matthias Bachinger]]\n|6\u20134, 6\u20133\n|-\n|bgcolor=#98fb98|Win\n|<small>9\u20133</small>\n|[[2018 Canberra Challenger \u2013 Singles|{{dts|Jan 2018}}]]\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|[[Canberra Challenger|Canberra]], Australia\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|Challenger\n|Hard \n|{{flagicon|HUN}} [[M\u00e1rton Fucsovics]]\n|5\u20137, 6\u20134, 6\u20133\n|-\n|bgcolor=#98fb98|Win\n|<small>8\u20133</small>\n|[[2019 Cary Challenger \u2013 Singles|{{dts|Sep 2019}}]]\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|[[Cary Challenger|Cary]], USA\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|Challenger\n|Hard\n|{{flagicon|USA}} [[Michael Mmoh]]\n|6\u20132, 6\u20137, 6\u20133\n|}\n\n=== Doubles: 2 (1\u20131) ===\n{|\n|-valign=top\n|\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:97%\n!Legend (Doubles)\n|-bgcolor=e5d1cb\n|-bgcolor=moccasin\n|ATP Challenger Tour (1\u20131)\n|-bgcolor=cffcff\n|ITF Futures Tour (0\u20130)\n|}\n|\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:97%\n!Titles by Surface\n|-\n|Hard (1\u20130)\n|-\n|Clay (0\u20131)\n|-\n|Grass (0\u20130)\n|-\n|Carpet (0\u20130)\n|}\n|}\n\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n!Result\n!class=\"unsortable\"|W\u2013L\n!{{ns}}Date{{ns}}\n!Tournament\n!Tier\n!Surface\n!Partner\n!Opponents\n!class=\"unsortable\"|Score\n|-\n|bgcolor=FFA07A|Loss\n|<small>0\u20131</small>\n|{{dts