dy Ram]]\n|3\u20136, 3\u20136\n|-\n|bgcolor=FFA07A|Loss\n|<small>0\u20135</small>\n|[[2013 China Open \u2013 Men's Doubles|{{dts|Oct 2013}}]]\n|style=\"background:#D4F1C5;\"|[[China Open (tennis)|China Open]], China\n|style=\"background:#D4F1C5;\"|500 Series\n|Hard\n|{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Fabio Fognini]]\n|{{flagicon|BLR}} [[Max Mirnyi]]<br>{{flagicon|ROU}} [[Horia Tec\u0103u]]\n|4\u20136, 2\u20136\n|-\n|bgcolor=98FB98|Win\n|<small>1\u20135</small>\n|[[2016 Dubai Tennis Championships \u2013 Men's Doubles|{{dts|Feb 2016}}]]\n|style=\"background:#D4F1C5;\"|[[Dubai Tennis Championships]], UAE\n|style=\"background:#D4F1C5;\"|500 Series\n|Hard\n|{{flagicon|ITA}} [[Simone Bolelli]]\n|{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Feliciano L\u00f3pez]]<br>{{flagicon|ESP}} [[Marc L\u00f3pez]]\n|6\u20132, 3\u20136, [14\u201312]\n|}\n\n\n== Challenger and Futures finals ==\n\n=== Singles: 12 (9\u20133) ===\n{|\n|-valign=top\n|\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:97%\n!Legend (Singles)\n|-bgcolor=moccasin\n|ATP Challenger Tour (8\u20133)\n|-bgcolor=#cffcff\n|ITF Futures Tour (1\u20130)\n|}\n|\n{|class=wikitable style=font-size:97%\n!Titles by Surface\n|-\n|Hard (6\u20131)\n|-\n|Clay (2\u20131)\n|-\n|Grass (0\u20130)\n|-\n|Carpet (1\u20131)\n|}\n|}\n\n{|class=\"sortable wikitable\"\n!Result\n!class=\"unsortable\"|W\u2013L\n!{{ns}}Date{{ns}}\n!Tournament\n!Tier\n!Surface\n!Opponent\n!class=\"unsortable\"|Score\n|-\n|bgcolor=#98fb98|Win\n|<small>1\u20130</small>\n|{{dts|Jan 2003}}\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Germany F1C, [[Munich]]\n|style=\"background:#cffcff;\"|Futures\n|Carpet (i)\n|{{flagicon|GER}} [[Lars \u00dcbel]]\n|6\u20134, 7\u20135\n|-\n|bgcolor=FFA07A|Loss\n|<small>1\u20131</small>\n|{{dts|Jul 2003}}\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|[[BMW Tennis Championship|Sunrise]], USA\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"|Challenger\n|Hard\n|{{flagicon|FRA}} [[Ga\u00ebl Monfils]]\n|3\u20136, 6\u20131, 1\u20136\n|-\n|bgcolor=FFA07A|Loss\n|<small>1\u20132</small>\n|{{dts|Mar 2007}}\n|style=\"background:moccasin;\"